metadata.name: Limited Edition Jim Jones G.O.A.T. Collectible
metadata.description: Greatness demands sacrifice. Before the Glory there's the Grind. The Greatest Of All Time! It gets no higher than G.O.A.T. In a proud winner's stance, the Limited Edition Jim Jones G.O.A.T. NFT is blessed with the midas touch. The all gold goat with a diamond studded spine and leg joints reps the VAMPLIFE Fitted Cap. This NFT reminds us that there is a G.O.A.T.  inside all of us waiting to be discovered and unleashed.
